/*
 * main.c
 *
 * GLUT/OpenGL CAD demo — Icons, immediate tooltips (gelb mit schwarzem Rand),
 * and GPU grid rendering via a fragment shader for speed and simpler code.
 *
 * Compile:
 *   gcc main.c -o cad -lGL -lGLU -lglut -lm
 *
 * Controls:
 *   - Click toolbar buttons: Center / + / - / Reset / Grid / Snap
 *   - Left drag inside content: pan
 *   - Right click inside content: add point (snaps if Snap enabled)
 *   - Mouse wheel or +/-: animated zoom (from content center)
 *   - 'u': cycle manual unit (switches auto off)
 *   - 'a': toggle auto unit selection
 *   - Esc: quit
 *
 * Notes:
 *   - Grid is rendered by a GLSL fragment shader (faster, simpler).
 *   - Toolbar icons are drawn procedurally (no external images).
 *   - Tooltips show immediately (no delay), yellow background, black border.
 */
